{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882413715,"sessionID":"ses_2852a811cffeR7DoAWEXcjqL5o","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad7215d001Wlgt0PqdegkO16","messageID":"msg_d7ad70689001xE780nuVY3YEWl","sessionID":"ses_2852a811cffeR7DoAWEXcjqL5o","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:19","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","offset":150,"limit":200},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n150: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n151: в”Ӯ Initialize    в”Ӯ\n152: в”Ӯ Dependencies  в”Ӯ\n153: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n154:         в”Ӯ\n155:         в–ј\n156: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n157: в”Ӯ Start Service в”Ӯ\n158: в”Ӯ (blocking)    в”Ӯ\n159: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n160:         в”Ӯ\n161:         в–ј\n162: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n163: в”Ӯ Wait for      в”Ӯ\n164: в”Ӯ SIGINT/SIGTERMв”Ӯ\n165: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n166:         в”Ӯ\n167:         в–ј\n168: в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\n169: в”Ӯ Graceful      в”Ӯ\n170: в”Ӯ Shutdown      в”Ӯ\n171: в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n172:         в”Ӯ\n173:         в–ј\n174:     Exit(0)\n175: ```\n176: \n177: ### agentd Startup Flow\n178: \n179: ```\n180: main()\n181:     в”Ӯ\n182:     в–ј\n183: Parse flags: --kubeconfig, --sync-period\n184:     в”Ӯ\n185:     в–ј\n186: ctrl.GetConfigOrDie() // K8s config\n187:     в”Ӯ\n188:     в–ј\n189: scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n190:     в”Ӯ\n191:     в–ј\n192: Add Sandbox v1alpha1 to scheme\n193:     в”Ӯ\n194:     в–ј\n195: ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.Options{\n196:     Scheme: scheme,\n197:     SyncPeriod: syncPeriod,\n198: })\n199:     в”Ӯ\n200:     в–ј\n201: agentd.NewReconciler(mgr.GetClient())\n202:     в”Ӯ\n203:     в–ј\n204: SetupWithManager(mgr)\n205:     в”Ӯ\n206:     в–ј\n207: mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())\n208: ```\n209: \n210: ### router Startup Flow\n211: \n212: ```\n213: main()\n214:     в”Ӯ\n215:     в–ј\n216: Parse flags: --port, --redis-addr, --workload-manager\n217:     в”Ӯ\n218:     в–ј\n219: Validate required flags\n220:     в”Ӯ\n221:     в–ј\n222: redis.NewClient(redisAddr)\n223:     в”Ӯ\n224:     в–ј\n225: store := router.NewSessionStore(redis)\n226:     в”Ӯ\n227:     в–ј\n228: gin.New()\n229:     в”Ӯ\n230:     в–ј\n231: router.SetupRoutes(engine, store, workloadMgrURL)\n232:     в”Ӯ\n233:     в–ј\n234: http.ListenAndServe()\n235:     в”Ӯ\n236:     в–ј\n237: Signal handling for graceful shutdown\n238: ```\n239: \n240: ### workload-manager Startup Flow\n241: \n242: ```\n243: main()\n244:     в”Ӯ\n245:     в–ј\n246: Parse flags: --port, --kubeconfig, --redis-addr, --default-image\n247:     в”Ӯ\n248:     в–ј\n249: ctrl.GetConfigOrDie()\n250:     в”Ӯ\n251:     в–ј\n252: scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n253: Add AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter to scheme\n254:     в”Ӯ\n255:     в–ј\n256: ctrl.NewManager(...)\n257:     в”Ӯ\n258:     в–ј\n259: workloadmanager.NewController(mgr, redis, config)\n260:     в”Ӯ\n261:     в–ј\n262: Setup HTTP API server on --port\n263:     в”Ӯ\n264:     в–ј\n265: Start both controller and HTTP server\n266: ```\n267: \n268: ### picod Startup Flow\n269: \n270: ```\n271: main()\n272:     в”Ӯ\n273:     в–ј\n274: Parse flags: --port, --workspace\n275:     в”Ӯ\n276:     в–ј\n277: Resolve workspace to absolute path\n278: Create if not exists\n279:     в”Ӯ\n280:     в–ј\n281: Validate workspace is writable\n282:     в”Ӯ\n283:     в–ј\n284: http.NewServeMux()\n285:     в”Ӯ\n286:     в–ј\n287: Register handlers:\n288:   - /execute (code execution)\n289:   - /upload (file upload)\n290:   - /download (file download)\n291:   - /exec (interactive exec)\n292:     в”Ӯ\n293:     в–ј\n294: http.ListenAndServe()\n295: ```\n296: \n297: ---\n298: \n299: ## Interface\n300: \n301: ### agentd Flags\n302: \n303: | Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n304: |------|------|---------|-------------|\n305: | `--kubeconfig` | string | \"\" | Path to kubeconfig (empty = in-cluster) |\n306: | `--sync-period` | duration | 5m | Full sync period for all sandboxes |\n307: | `--graceful-timeout` | duration | 30s | Graceful shutdown timeout |\n308: | `--help` | bool | false | Print usage and exit |\n309: \n310: ### router Flags\n311: \n312: | Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n313: |------|------|---------|-------------|\n314: | `--port` | int | 8080 | HTTP server port |\n315: | `--debug` | bool | false | Enable debug logging |\n316: | `--redis-addr` | string | (required) | Redis/Valkey server address |\n317: | `--workload-manager` | string | (required) | Workload manager URL |\n318: | `--graceful-timeout` | duration | 30s | Graceful shutdown timeout |\n319: | `--help` | bool | false | Print usage and exit |\n320: \n321: ### workload-manager Flags\n322: \n323: | Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n324: |------|------|---------|-------------|\n325: | `--port` | int | 8080 | HTTP API server port |\n326: | `--kubeconfig` | string | \"\" | Path to kubeconfig (empty = in-cluster) |\n327: | `--redis-addr` | string | (required) | Redis/Valkey server address |\n328: | `--default-image` | string | \"ubuntu:22.04\" | Default sandbox image |\n329: | `--namespace` | string | \"default\" | Default namespace |\n330: | `--graceful-timeout` | duration | 30s | Graceful shutdown timeout |\n331: | `--help` | bool | false | Print usage and exit |\n332: \n333: ### picod Flags\n334: \n335: | Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n336: |------|------|---------|-------------|\n337: | `--port` | int | 8080 | HTTP server port |\n338: | `--workspace` | string | \".\" | Workspace root directory |\n339: | `--read-header-timeout` | duration | 10s | HTTP read header timeout |\n340: | `--help` | bool | false | Print usage and exit |\n341: \n342: ---\n343: \n344: ## Error Handling\n345: \n346: ### Error Types\n347: \n348: | Error | Description | Binary |\n349: |-------|-------------|--------|\n\n(Showing lines 150-349 of 615. Use offset=350 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ Initialize    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ Dependencies  в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n        в”Ӯ\n        в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ Start Service в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ (blocking)    в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n        в”Ӯ\n        в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ Wait for      в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ SIGINT/SIGTERMв”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\n        в”Ӯ\n        в–ј\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ Graceful      в”Ӯ","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882413682,"end":1775882413712}}}}
