{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882438584,"sessionID":"ses_2852a811cffeR7DoAWEXcjqL5o","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad7826c001IYcORoJSm4Cu6B","messageID":"msg_d7ad751ab001z0yXYnrtrP0lXf","sessionID":"ses_2852a811cffeR7DoAWEXcjqL5o","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:21","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","limit":100,"offset":550},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n550: ### Startup Verification (Local)\n551: \n552: ```bash\n553: # Test picod (no external deps)\n554: ./bin/picod --port=18080 &\n555: sleep 1\n556: curl http://localhost:18080/health || echo \"Health check not implemented yet\"\n557: kill %1\n558: \n559: # Test agentd (requires K8s config, will fail gracefully)\n560: ./bin/agentd --kubeconfig=/dev/null 2>&1 | head -5\n561: \n562: # Test with missing required flags\n563: ./bin/router 2>&1 | grep -q \"required\" && echo \"Flag validation works\"\n564: ```\n565: \n566: ### Graceful Shutdown Test\n567: \n568: ```bash\n569: # Test graceful shutdown\n570: timeout 2 ./bin/picod --port=18081 &\n571: sleep 0.5\n572: kill -TERM %1\n573: wait %1\n574: echo \"Exit code: $?\"  # Should be 0\n575: ```\n576: \n577: ### Docker Build Verification\n578: \n579: ```bash\n580: # Build container images\n581: make docker-build\n582: \n583: # Verify images\n584: docker images | grep agentcube\n585: ```\n586: \n587: ---\n588: \n589: ## References\n590: \n591: - [AR-019 Delta Spec](changes/AR-019/delta-spec.md) вҖ” Detailed requirements\n592: - [client-go Library](deployment/client-go.md) вҖ” Kubernetes client patterns\n593: - [Deployment Design](deployment/design.md) вҖ” Helm charts and Dockerfiles\n594: - [CLI Toolkit Design](cli-toolkit/design.md) вҖ” Python CLI design\n595: - [project.md](project.md) вҖ” Project context and architecture\n596: \n597: ---\n598: \n599: ## Success Criteria\n600: \n601: 1. вң… All 4 binaries compile without errors\n602: 2. вң… Each binary prints help with `--help` flag\n603: 3. вң… Each binary validates required flags and exits with error if missing\n604: 4. вң… agentd starts controller-runtime manager with Sandbox reconciler\n605: 5. вң… router starts Gin HTTP server and connects to Redis\n606: 6. вң… workload-manager starts controller and HTTP API server\n607: 7. вң… picod starts HTTP server and initializes workspace\n608: 8. вң… All binaries handle SIGINT/SIGTERM for graceful shutdown\n609: 9. вң… Exit codes are correct (0 for success, non-zero for errors)\n610: 10. вң… Docker builds succeed for all binaries\n611: 11. вң… Binaries log startup messages with version and configuration\n612: \n613: ---\n614: \n615: *AR-019 вҖ” Module: cmd вҖ” Language: Go вҖ” Size: M*\n\n(End of file - total 615 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"### Startup Verification (Local)\n\n```bash\n# Test picod (no external deps)\n./bin/picod --port=18080 &\nsleep 1\ncurl http://localhost:18080/health || echo \"Health check not implemented yet\"\nkill %1\n\n# Test agentd (requires K8s config, will fail gracefully)\n./bin/agentd --kubeconfig=/dev/null 2>&1 | head -5\n\n# Test with missing required flags\n./bin/router 2>&1 | grep -q \"required\" && echo \"Flag validation works\"\n```\n\n### Graceful Shutdown Test\n\n```bash\n# Test graceful shutdown","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882438546,"end":1775882438580}}}}
