{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882680022,"sessionID":"ses_2852a811cffeR7DoAWEXcjqL5o","part":{"id":"prt_d7adb3169001Vpkbh3Tc3XTYNu","messageID":"msg_d7adb00d9001nzJL0Whigt2SfB","sessionID":"ses_2852a811cffeR7DoAWEXcjqL5o","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_functions.bash:26","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"head -100 /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/cmd/design.md","description":"Verify design.md content"},"output":"# AR-019 Design: CLI Binary Entry Points\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-019  \n**Module:** `cmd`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M (Medium)\n\nThis module provides the CLI binary entry points for the 4 core AgentCube components. Each binary provides a standalone executable that initializes its respective service with proper configuration, dependency wiring, and graceful shutdown handling.\n\n### Components\n\n| Binary | Purpose | Package Dependency |\n|--------|---------|-------------------|\n| `agentd` | Idle cleanup controller for AgentRuntime resources | `pkg/agentd` |\n| `router` | HTTP session routing proxy with JWT authentication | `pkg/router` |\n| `workload-manager` | Sandbox orchestration controller with CRD management | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| `picod` | Sandbox daemon for code execution inside sandbox pods | `pkg/picod` |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Design\n\n```\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ                        AgentCube Platform                                    в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ                                                                              в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ  в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”